  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dd1\u0db8\u0da7 \u0d8b\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dcf\u0dc4 \u0d9a\u0dc5 13 \u0dc4\u0dd0\u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd2 \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dd2 \u0daf\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A 13-year-old boy was arrested for trying to rob money",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Bandaragama Police say that a 13-year-old boy jumped into a market in Namalwa area of \u200b\u200bBandaragama and attempted to rob the shop owner with a knife, injured the owner of the store who prevented him from doing so, and was arrested while running away and hiding.",
        "As a result of that attack, the 33-year-old shop owner sustained injuries on her abdomen and right arm. The owner of the store when the suspect boy entered the store and reached into the drawer. The police said that the owner of the store was injured and ran away with a small knife that he had in his hand.",
        "A police officer said that the complaint filed by the owner of the store states that the suspect boy had tried to steal money from her store on several occasions before.",
        "Police said that the injured woman was admitted to the Bandaragama District Hospital and received treatment and the doctor who examined her said that the cuts were not serious.",
        "The police officer further said that the suspect boy was taken and handed over to his parents after recording his statements and that he will be presented to the forensic medical officer of Panadura Base Hospital today."
      ],
